  "line_count": 2,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00031:a4f4ee8f0af7]]\n五个问题不是孤立求值，而是沿着[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00032:64ff06c5c1a7]]这条生态传导链展开。本文既要描述禁渔带来的恢复趋势，也要解释新失衡现象，并回答[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00033:4a1ed1664a80]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P00034:dad49176ea50]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P00035:f998bc3bd7bf]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P00036:aed6d1589b1e]]。\n",
